Add `decree commit-check`: a deterministic trailer-coverage gate that reports how many in-flight-governed changed paths carry a matching `Implements:/Refs:/Fixes:` trailer. Resolves changed paths from `--diff`/`--diff-base`/staged and trailers from `--diff-base` (squash-safe CI mode) or `--message` (commit-msg hook mode); advisory by default, gateable via `--strict` or `--min-coverage N`, with a stable `--json` contract.
